evel":2,"id":"工作流程"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"工作流程"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当用户触发此 skill 时，请按照以下步骤执行："}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"第一步分析用户输入"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第一步：分析用户输入"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果用户只是一句话，直接将其作为海报主体文字。 如果用户输入较长，提取出最具冲击力的一句话作为大标题（标语），其余作为副标题或说明文字。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"第二步确认设计风格可选"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第二步：确认设计风格（可选）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果用户没有指定风格，默认使用现代、简洁、对比强烈的风格（如黑色背景+亮黄色/白色文字，类似知识分享类海报）。 如果需要，可以向用户确认：\"我为您构思了深色极简科技风，包含大字高亮设计，是否可以直接为您生成？\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"第三步生成代码并渲染"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第三步：生成代码并渲染"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编写高质量的 HTML 和内联 CSS 代码。 要求："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"使用现代字体（如 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"system-ui"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"-apple-system"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"PingFang SC"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Microsoft YaHei"},{"type":"text","text":"）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"良好的留白（Padding/Margin）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"强烈的视觉层次感（大字号主标题，高亮关键词）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"合适的背景色和文字颜色对比度"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"提供代码后，指导用户如何查看效果（例如：保存为 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".html"},{"type":"text","text":" 文件在浏览器中打开，或者如果我们在具有预览能力的环境中，直接渲染）。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"最佳实践提示"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"最佳实践提示"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"高亮关键词"},{"type":"text","text":"：对于一句话，找出其中的动词或核心名词，使用不同的颜色（如亮黄色）进行高亮，增加视觉冲击力。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"排版对齐"},{"type":"text","text":"：通常左对齐或居中对齐看起来最专业。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"添加装饰"},{"type":"text","text":"：可以添加简单的引号图标 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"\""},{"type":"text","text":"，或者上下分隔线，增加海报感。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"副标题设计"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"副标题字号应小于主标题，通常使用16px左右"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"颜色使用灰色（如 #888）以区分层级"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"副标题应对主标题进行解释、扩展或补充，提供更深层的思考"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"严格控制字数在15字以内，保持简洁有力"}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"示例-HTML-模板结构"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"示例 HTML 模板结构"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<style>\n  body { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; background: #333; margin: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif; }\n  .poster { width: 400px; height: 600px; background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 40px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; }\n  .quote-mark { font-size: 80px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); position: absolute; top: 40px; left: 40px; line-height: 1; }\n  .main-text { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 20px; z-index: 1; }\n  .highlight { color: #ccff00; } /* 亮黄绿色高亮 */\n  .sub-text { font-size: 16px; color: #888; line-height: 1.6; }\n  .author { margin-top: auto; font-size: 14px; color: #ccc; border-top: 1px solid #333; padding-top: 20px; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"poster\">\n    <div class=\"quote-mark\">\"</div>\n    <div class=\"main-text\">在这个时代<br>你还在<span class=\"highlight\">考虑钱</span><br>就<span class=\"highlight\">落后了</span></div>\n    <div class=\"sub-text\">用AI杠杆放大你的产能</div>\n    <div class=\"author\">@周鸿祎</div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}]}]}